OL,3,CReport warns of 'toxic cultures' and
OL,4,C'unacceptable behaviour' in fire
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FCultural change is happening too
OL,8,Fslowly in England's fire service, with
OL,9,F"abhorrent behaviour" such as sexism,
OL,10,Fracism and homophobia widespread
OL,11,Facross brigades, a report has warned.
OL,13,FAn investigation by His Majesty's
OL,14,FInspectorate of Constabulary and Fire
OL,15,Fand Secure Services (HMICFRS) found
OL,16,Fthat while there were early signs of
OL,17,Fimprovement in the culture at fire
OL,18,Fservices, "too much unacceptable
OL,19,Fbehaviour remains."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
