OL,3,CReport warns of 'toxic cultures' and
OL,4,C'unacceptable behaviour' in fire
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FThe report, which focuses just on
OL,8,FEngland, found instances of sexist,
OL,9,Fracist and homophobic language, being
OL,10,Fused mostly among groups of
OL,11,Ffirefighters who work closely
OL,12,Ftogether, known as "watches."
OL,14,FStaff described examples of "toxic
OL,15,Fcultures" where managers didn't
OL,16,Fchallenge poor behaviour in order to
OL,17,F"remain popular."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
