OL,3,CReport warns of 'toxic cultures' and
OL,4,C'unacceptable behaviour' in fire
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FThe inspector expressed significant
OL,8,Fconcern about a "lack of confidence"
OL,9,Fin misconduct processes, with managers
OL,10,Fnot properly trained to deal with
OL,11,Funacceptable behaviour.
OL,13,FHis Majesty's Inspector of Fire and
OL,14,FRescue Services Roy Wilshertold ITV
OL,15,FNews: "Cultural change does take time,
OL,16,Fbut change isn't happening quickly
OL,17,Fenough"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
