OL,3,CReport warns of 'toxic cultures' and
OL,4,C'unacceptable behaviour' in fire
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FMr Wilsher said there was a big issue
OL,8,Faround people lacking confidence to
OL,9,Freport negative behaviour, adding:
OL,10,F"People are afraid that their
OL,11,Fconfidentiality will be breached, and
OL,12,Fwe've actually had examples of people
OL,13,Fbeing told their careers will be
OL,14,Flimited if they do raise issues."
OL,16,FThe inspector is urging fire services
OL,17,Fand the authorities that govern them
OL,18,Fto introduce 15 recommendations in
OL,19,Forder to tackle the crisis in culture.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
