OL,3,CReport warns of 'toxic cultures' and
OL,4,C'unacceptable behaviour' in fire
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FThey include introducing better
OL,8,Ftraining and support for staff on
OL,9,Finvestigating misconduct, and creating
OL,10,Fa "professional standards function"
OL,11,Fwithin each service that staff have
OL,12,Faccess to.
OL,14,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "The
OL,15,Ffindings from the Inspectorate's
OL,16,Freport are deeply concerning.
OL,18,F"There is no space for misconduct in
OL,19,Four Fire and Rescue Services, and we
OL,20,Fexpect it to be addressed at the
OL,21,Fearliest opportunity.
