OL,3,CReport warns of 'toxic cultures' and
OL,4,C'unacceptable behaviour' in fire
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"We will be carefully considering the
OL,8,Frecommendations, and will be kept
OL,9,Fupdated by HMICFRS on progress made.
OL,11,F"We will also continue to work with
OL,12,Fclosely with the fire sector to ensure
OL,13,Fthat the highest levels of integrity
OL,14,Fare maintained across services."
OL,16,FITV News' UK Editor Paul Brand has
OL,17,Freported extensively on toxic
OL,18,Fcultures, harassment, and bullying
OL,19,Fwithin fire services.
