OL,3,CReport warns of 'toxic cultures' and
OL,4,C'unacceptable behaviour' in fire
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FA series of investigations by ITV News
OL,8,Fhas uncovered sexual harassment and
OL,9,Fabuse of women at fire and rescue
OL,10,Fservices including South Wales, Dorset
OL,11,Fand Wiltshire, Tyne and Wear and most
OL,12,Frecently, in Shropshire.
OL,14,FTwo independent reviews sparked by ITV
OL,15,FNews' reporting have already concluded
OL,16,Fthat there is a toxic culture in some
OL,17,Ffire services.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
