OL,3,CReport warns of 'toxic cultures' and
OL,4,C'unacceptable behaviour' in fire
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FEarlier this year, the Chief Fire
OL,8,FOfficer of South Wales Fire Service
OL,9,Fwas forced to retire (on full pension)
OL,10,Fafter a damning review into his
OL,11,Forganisation, with the service
OL,12,Fsubsequently put into special measures
OL,13,Fby the Welsh government.
OL,15,FIn Dorset and Wiltshire, a review
OL,16,Ffound that misogyny and sexism was
OL,17,Frife within the service, despite the
OL,18,FChief Fire Officer previously telling
OL,19,FITV News that his organisation "does
OL,20,Fnot have a problem with women".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
