OL,3,CReport warns of 'toxic cultures' and
OL,4,C'unacceptable behaviour' in fire
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FIn May this year the Home Affairs
OL,8,FSelect Committee declared the fire and
OL,9,Frescue service "institutionally
OL,10,Fmisogynistic, racist and homophobic."
OL,12,FMr Wilsher would not use the word
OL,13,F"institutional" to describe the
OL,14,Fissues, adding: "We try not to call
OL,15,Fthat out on different organisations
OL,16,Fbecause people concentrate on that
OL,17,Fthen, rather than what's happening and
OL,18,Fwhat needs to change."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
