OL,3,CReport warns of 'toxic cultures' and
OL,4,C'unacceptable behaviour' in fire
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FThe Committee also recommended giving
OL,8,FHMICFRS more enforcement powers in
OL,9,Forder to improve the sector, which the
OL,10,Finspector said he hopes the new home
OL,11,Fsecretary will introduce.
OL,13,F"At the moment the power is in our
OL,14,Fvoice, we write reports, we highlight
OL,15,Fthings... but we have no other powers.
OL,16,FSo it's not sweeping powers we're
OL,17,Fcalling for, but we do want to make
OL,18,Fpeople do things if we recommend they
OL,19,Fshould happen."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
